{"tid":2097853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇經我同意用我信用咭買點數咭！！！！！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！  ！ ！ ！  ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！","createTime":"2020-07-07T05:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T10:05:55.000Z","uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d12945ef4e916760839fab9848bc83ef1f4edaed","tid":2097853,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">屋企人冇信用卡，之前問過我一次話佢朋友想充值（~$800)，叫我借信用卡比佢買點數打機，我拒絕左，原因係我驚買呢d之後會容易比人盜用張咭同埋收多左錢。(我不嬲唔會逐條數check既，大數唔爭太多就每月照找）而且7仔都有點數咭買，點解一定要我用credit card ?<br />\n<br />\n之後今日岩岩屋企人同我講佢用左我張咭幫朋友買左點數，問我拎户口入番錢比我。我&lt;下&gt;左，我冇爆佢，不過有表達我好不滿。但我其實勁嬲，點解我話左唔比都要照做，佢話因爲朋友太煩所以先幫。我真係嬲左，煩就要幫，就無視我既說話同感受？唔爆佢係費事比佢話我小事化大，斤斤計較<br />\n<br />\n(佢有我信用咭資料係因為之前借過比佢買機票)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呻完</div></span></strong>"},{"pid":"acd9b2870e1028fe062730295b52e03b6dd963ac","tid":2097853,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjOJ8aL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjOJ8aL.png&h=66578880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"3505f1687f0cf038dc5c399798a9f2edb6a3828e","tid":2097853,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ddc98cc58a03ff030fd35d0763a946a4a77630","tid":2097853,"uid":56148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"我借我細佬張咭用完都即刻delete資料<br />\n你屋企人咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345ca74769a91525b12accefcbd91c677d674c39","tid":2097853,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4ddc98cc58a03ff030fd35d0763a946a4a77630","tid":2097853,"uid":56148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"我借我細佬張咭用完都即刻dele